# Trivy ignore list — keep in sync with pnpm `auditConfig.ignoreGhsas` (package.json).
#
# These are all advisories for `tar` reached ONLY via apps/mobile > expo > @expo/cli > tar
# (the Expo build CLI, a BUILD-TIME dev tool — it is NOT shipped in the mobile app
# bundle or any runtime). @expo/cli requires tar's v6 API, so we cannot bump to the
# patched tar >=7.5.x without breaking `expo prebuild`. Accepted, build-tool-only risk.
# Re-evaluate when @expo/cli supports tar 7.
#
# node-tar (path traversal / arbitrary file write family):
